---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Contract-Driven Development — Eidos AGI"
  description="Agents execute specs, not vibes. Every decision has a confidence level. Every action traces back to a contract."
>
    <article class="prose-page">
      <header class="page-hero">
        <h1>Contract-Driven<br />Development</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Agents execute specs, not vibes.</p>
      </header>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>The problem</h2>
        <p>When an AI agent runs a task, it makes decisions. Which approach to use, what to prioritize, when to stop. Most of those decisions happen in conversation — unrecorded, unreviewable, unreproducible. The agent improvises. Sometimes it improvises well. Sometimes it doesn't. Either way, there's no receipt.</p>
        <p>Contract-driven development replaces improvisation with specification. Every decision has a confidence level. Every action traces back to a contract. Nothing runs on "inferred" — it runs on "proven."</p>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>The confidence model</h2>
        <p>Every fact an agent depends on carries a confidence level:</p>
        <table class="cdd-table">
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Level</th><th>Meaning</th><th>Can build on?</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td class="cdd-level cdd-proven">proven</td><td>Tested in production, confirmed working</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="cdd-level cdd-tested">tested</td><td>Validated against real system, not yet production</td><td>Yes, with monitoring</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="cdd-level cdd-researched">researched</td><td>From documentation, not verified</td><td>Verify first</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="cdd-level cdd-inferred">inferred</td><td>Guessed from similar systems</td><td>No — must verify</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="cdd-level cdd-unknown">unknown</td><td>No information available</td><td>No — must discover</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="cdd-level cdd-blocked">blocked</td><td>Known to exist but can't verify</td><td>No — must unblock</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <!-- Confidence spectrum -->
        <div class="cdd-diagram">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 500 100" fill="none" role="img" aria-label="Confidence spectrum from blocked (red) through unknown, inferred, researched, tested, to proven (green)">
            <!-- Spectrum bar -->
            <rect x="30" y="30" width="70" height="24" rx="2" fill="var(--color-danger)" opacity="0.7"/>
            <rect x="102" y="30" width="70" height="24" rx="2" fill="var(--color-danger)" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="174" y="30" width="70" height="24" rx="2" fill="var(--color-muted)" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="246" y="30" width="70" height="24" rx="2" fill="var(--color-primary)" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="318" y="30" width="70" height="24" rx="2" fill="var(--color-secondary)" opacity="0.6"/>
            <rect x="390" y="30" width="70" height="24" rx="2" fill="var(--color-command)" opacity="0.7"/>

            <!-- Labels -->
            <text class="conf-label" x="65" y="46" text-anchor="middle">blocked</text>
            <text class="conf-label" x="137" y="46" text-anchor="middle">unknown</text>
            <text class="conf-label" x="209" y="46" text-anchor="middle">inferred</text>
            <text class="conf-label" x="281" y="46" text-anchor="middle">researched</text>
            <text class="conf-label" x="353" y="46" text-anchor="middle">tested</text>
            <text class="conf-label" x="425" y="46" text-anchor="middle">proven</text>

            <!-- Direction arrow -->
            <line class="conf-arrow" x1="30" y1="72" x2="460" y2="72"/>
            <polygon class="conf-head" points="454,66 464,72 454,78"/>
            <text class="conf-dir" x="245" y="90" text-anchor="middle">increasing confidence</text>

            <!-- Threshold marker -->
            <line x1="318" y1="25" x2="318" y2="58" stroke="var(--color-text)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3 2"/>
            <text class="conf-threshold" x="318" y="20" text-anchor="middle">can build</text>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <p>The readiness of a system is the lowest confidence level of its constituent parts. One "unknown" field means the system is not production-ready, even if 99% of fields are proven.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>The trilogy implements it</h2>

        <!-- Trilogy pipeline -->
        <div class="cdd-diagram">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 500 80" fill="none" role="img" aria-label="Trilogy pipeline: research.md earns decisions, visionlog records contracts, ike.md executes within them">
            <rect class="cdd-pipe-node" x="10" y="15" width="140" height="50" rx="3"/>
            <text class="cdd-pipe-label" x="80" y="45" text-anchor="middle">research.md</text>
            <text class="cdd-pipe-sub" x="80" y="32" text-anchor="middle">EARN DECISIONS</text>

            <rect class="cdd-pipe-node" x="180" y="15" width="140" height="50" rx="3"/>
            <text class="cdd-pipe-label" x="250" y="45" text-anchor="middle">visionlog</text>
            <text class="cdd-pipe-sub" x="250" y="32" text-anchor="middle">RECORD CONTRACTS</text>

            <rect class="cdd-pipe-node" x="350" y="15" width="140" height="50" rx="3"/>
            <text class="cdd-pipe-label" x="420" y="45" text-anchor="middle">ike.md</text>
            <text class="cdd-pipe-sub" x="420" y="32" text-anchor="middle">EXECUTE</text>

            <line class="cdd-pipe-arrow" x1="150" y1="40" x2="180" y2="40"/>
            <polygon class="cdd-pipe-head" points="174,34 184,40 174,46"/>
            <line class="cdd-pipe-arrow" x1="320" y1="40" x2="350" y2="40"/>
            <polygon class="cdd-pipe-head" points="344,34 354,40 344,46"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="cdd-trio">
          <div class="cdd-trio-item">
            <h3>visionlog</h3>
            <p>Records the contracts — guardrails, goals, ADRs. These are the constraints all execution must honor.</p>
            <code>pip install visionlog-md</code>
          </div>
          <div class="cdd-trio-item">
            <h3>research.md</h3>
            <p>Earns the decisions with evidence. Candidates scored against locked criteria. The research is the receipt.</p>
            <code>pip install research-md</code>
          </div>
          <div class="cdd-trio-item">
            <h3>ike.md</h3>
            <p>Executes tasks within the contracts. Definition of Done is explicit, not assumed.</p>
            <code>pip install ike-md</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>What changes</h2>
        <div class="cdd-changes">
          <div>
            <h3>Without contracts</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Agent picks an approach based on training data</li>
              <li>Decisions happen in conversation, lost after session</li>
              <li>No one knows why a choice was made</li>
              <li>"It worked" is the only success criterion</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>With contracts</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Agent reads guardrails before acting</li>
              <li>Decisions are scored, recorded, reviewable</li>
              <li>Every choice traces to evidence</li>
              <li>Definition of Done is explicit and auditable</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <p class="cdd-closing">Contract-driven development isn't a methodology to learn. It's three pip installs and a commitment to recording what matters.</p>
        <pre><code>pip install visionlog-md research-md ike-md</code></pre>
      </section>
    </article>
</Base>

<style is:global>
  /* CDD-specific components (not shared) */
  .cdd-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: var(--text-sm); margin: var(--space-6) 0; }
  .cdd-table th { text-align: left; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3); border-bottom: 2px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-muted) 20%, transparent); }
  .cdd-table td { padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3); border-bottom: var(--border-width) solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-muted) 10%, transparent); color: var(--color-muted); }
  .cdd-level { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-weight: var(--weight-medium); }
  .cdd-proven { color: var(--color-command); }
  .cdd-tested { color: var(--color-secondary); }
  .cdd-researched { color: var(--color-primary); }
  .cdd-inferred { color: var(--color-muted); }
  .cdd-unknown { color: var(--color-danger); }
  .cdd-blocked { color: var(--color-danger); }
  .cdd-trio { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--space-4); margin-top: var(--space-6); }
  .cdd-trio-item { background: var(--color-surface); padding: var(--space-6); border-radius: var(--radius-md); }
  .cdd-trio-item h3 { color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
  .cdd-trio-item p { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); }
  .cdd-trio-item code { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-command); }
  .cdd-changes { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-6); margin-top: var(--space-6); }
  .cdd-changes h3 { font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); }
  .cdd-changes ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .cdd-changes li { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-muted); padding: var(--space-2) 0; border-bottom: var(--border-width) solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-muted) 8%, transparent); line-height: var(--leading-normal); }
  .cdd-closing { font-size: var(--text-md); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin-bottom: var(--space-6); }
  .cdd-diagram { margin: var(--space-8) 0; max-width: 500px; }
  .cdd-diagram svg { width: 100%; height: auto; }
  .conf-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 9px; fill: var(--color-text); font-weight: 500; }
  .conf-arrow { stroke: var(--color-muted); stroke-width: 1; stroke-dasharray: 4 3; animation: conf-dash 2s linear infinite; }
  .conf-head { fill: var(--color-muted); }
  .conf-dir { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 8px; fill: var(--color-muted); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .conf-threshold { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 7px; fill: var(--color-text); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .cdd-pipe-node { fill: var(--color-surface); stroke: var(--color-primary); stroke-width: 1; }
  .cdd-pipe-label { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 13px; fill: var(--color-text); font-weight: 500; }
  .cdd-pipe-sub { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 7px; fill: var(--color-primary); letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
  .cdd-pipe-arrow { stroke: var(--color-primary); stroke-width: 1.5; stroke-dasharray: 4 3; animation: conf-dash 1.5s linear infinite; }
  .cdd-pipe-head { fill: var(--color-primary); }
  @keyframes conf-dash { to { stroke-dashoffset: -14; } }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .cdd-trio { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .cdd-changes { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .cdd-table { font-size: var(--text-xs); } }
</style>
